[I] The Famous Virtual Window Manager 3 the successor to fvwm2

[T] fvwm3 is a multiple large virtual desktop window manager. The successor to
[T] fvwm-2.6.x. Fvwm3 is intended to be extremely customizable and extendible
[T] while consuming a relatively small amount of resources.

[U] https://www.fvwm.org

[A] A lot of people <fvwm-workers@fvwm.org>
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/windowmanager
[F] CROSS

[L] GPL
[V] 1.1.5

[D] d9e88034319b779207d99f91a207a885f3586697a15a62b76d9feab2 fvwm3-1.1.5.tar.gz https://github.com/fvwmorg/fvwm3/archive/1.1.5/

hook_add postinstall 3 "register_wm fvwm3 FVWM3 $bindir/fvwm3"
